+  <text x="72" y="68" class="title">171Yb metastable nuclear-spin qubit: state paths to computational operations</text>
+  <text x="72" y="94" class="subtitle">Teaching map only: vertical placement separates manifolds and is not an energy scale. Colored arrows are driven or engineered channels; black arrows are decay or state flow.</text>
+
+  <rect x="72" y="124" width="1050" height="486" fill="#fbfcfb" stroke="#cbd5d0"/>
+  <text x="96" y="156" class="section">State map</text>
+  <text x="96" y="178" class="subtitle">The labels identify what each path does in a quantum-computing cycle, not merely its wavelength.</text>
+
+  <!-- State manifolds -->
+  <line x1="160" y1="530" x2="400" y2="530" class="rule"/>
+  <text x="96" y="537" class="level">1S0</text>
+  <text x="96" y="558" class="small">ground-state atom</text>
+
+  <line x1="260" y1="350" x2="480" y2="350" class="rule"/>
+  <text x="156" y="357" class="level">3P0</text>
+  <text x="156" y="378" class="small">metastable nuclear-spin qubit</text>
+
+  <line x1="500" y1="236" x2="660" y2="236" class="rule"/>
+  <text x="520" y="222" class="level">3P2</text>
+  <text x="520" y="258" class="small">readout shelving manifold</text>
+
+  <line x1="164" y1="236" x2="352" y2="236" class="rule"/>
+  <text x="96" y="222" class="level">3P1</text>
+  <text x="96" y="258" class="small">narrow-line cooling / imaging</text>
+
