+  <text x="96" y="588" class="tiny" fill="#53615d">Readout path shown is the Li et al. (2025) 649/770 nm Raman + 497 nm implementation. The 302/369 nm path is the Ma et al. (2023) Rydberg erasure-conversion implementation.</text>
